256.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">rawintanpin/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The fund outperformed its benchmark, the Bloomberg U.S. 1\u20133 Year Government/Credit Bond Index, for the three-month period that ended September 30, 2024. Duration, quality, and sector allocation were the largest contributors to performance, followed by issue selection. Curve positioning detracted from performance</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743918-allspring-short-term-bond-plus-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:20:00"}, {"id": "4743916", "title": "Allspring Short Duration Government Bond Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman writing notes in documents model on stack of coins, in business, saving money\" data-id=\"1430785838\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430